黄龙池”，是一基岩裂隙泉，水质清醇甘爽，终年不涸。 大洪山盛产葛根，葛粉为大洪山特产之一，葛粉是葛的块根，经水磨而澄取的淀粉，味甘，性大寒，无毒，归胃经，具有生津止渴、清热除烦的功效，可用于烦热、口渴、醉酒、喉痹的治疗。现代医学证明，该药物对高血压的控制有一定帮助。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IjriErcL3yNA1EAMaCDcxNTMyMzg3IKW3i4sGMAI4sAFAKHIJNDkxNjI3NzAyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"75 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-79d79d8c19f4ac796122f0dfc2732568_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"41_1635509489.381118","card_id":"Q_492454994","target":{"id":492454994,"title":"马上又到「双十一」囤书季，有哪些近两年新出的有深度有口碑的书籍推荐？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/492454994","type":"question","created":1634222852,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":117,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[53,113,1164,22528,49975],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4IjriErcL3yNA1EAMaCDcxNzE1OTI3IISGoYsGMAA4dUApcgk0OTI0NTQ5OTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"65 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0a00d904d0f1fd54ad4cdfff798e245_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"42_1635509489.3815348","card_id":"Q_30096854","target":{"id":30096854,"title":"能分享一下香港三大名校计算机专业硕士申请经验吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/30096854","type":"question","created":1430744866,"answer_count":25,"follower_count":165,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[205,69910],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj0IjriErcL3yNA1EAMaBzQyMjExOTMgot6dqgUwADilAUAqcggzMDA5Njg1NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"65 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ec0285810732093f9a